Architecture: all
Depends: xinit, xorg, plymouth, plymouth-themes, desktop-base, denios-core, denios-interface-common, denios-desktop-mate | denios-desktop-stub | denios-desktop-kde | denios-desktop-xfce | denios-desktop-i3 | denios-desktop-gnome | denios-kde | denios-xfce
